title: Crab Cakes
directions: Preheat oven broiler. Mix together crabmeat, parsley, almond flour, and crab seasoning. Beat together egg, mayonnaise, Worcestershire sauce, mustard, and lemon juice. Form into patties and place on a lightly greaser broiler pan or baking sheet.
Broil for 10-15 minutes, until lightly brown.
ingredients: ¾ tsp old bay – Maryland-style crab seasoning
